@startuml

' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
'  学生参加考试与自动评分时序图 (精简版)
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────

!theme plain
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "monospace"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam ArrowColor #000000
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #000000
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActorBorderColor #000000
skinparam SequenceBoxBorderColor #000000
skinparam SequenceBoxBackgroundColor #FFFFFF

title <b>学生参加考试与自动评分时序图</b>

actor 学生 as Student
participant "前端\n(Vue3 + Element Plus)" as Frontend
participant "ExamController\n(考试控制器)" as ExamController
participant "ExamService\n(考试服务)" as ExamService
participant "ExamSessionService\n(会话服务)" as ExamSessionService
database "MySQL\n(数据库)" as MySQL

== 1. 开始考试 ==
Student -> Frontend : 选择考试，点击开始
Frontend -> ExamController : POST /api/exams/{id}/start
ExamController -> ExamService : startExam(examId, studentId)
ExamService -> ExamService : 校验: 考试状态、时间、课程成员
ExamService -> ExamSessionService : save(session)\nstatus=IN_PROGRESS
ExamSessionService -> MySQL : INSERT INTO exam_sessions
MySQL --> ExamSessionService : 保存成功
ExamSessionService --> ExamService : 返回会话
ExamService --> ExamController : 返回 ExamSession
ExamController --> Frontend : 200 OK

== 2. 获取试题与答题 ==
Frontend -> ExamController : GET /api/exams/{id}/questions
ExamController -> ExamService : getExamQuestions(examId, studentId)
ExamService -> MySQL : SELECT questions (不含正确答案)
MySQL --> ExamService : 返回题目列表
ExamService --> ExamController : 返回题目 (已脱敏)
ExamController --> Frontend : 200 OK
Frontend --> Student : 展示试题，开始倒计时
Student -> Frontend : 逐题作答，定时自动保存

== 3. 提交与自动评分 ==
Student -> Frontend : 检查答案，点击交卷
Frontend -> ExamController : POST /api/exams/{id}/submit
ExamController -> ExamService : submitExam(examId, studentId, answers)
ExamService -> MySQL : SELECT questions (含正确答案)
MySQL --> ExamService : 返回题目及答案
ExamService -> ExamService : 客观题自动评分\n(单选/多选/判断/填空)\n主观题标记待评分
ExamService -> ExamSessionService : update(session)\nstatus=SUBMITTED, score=客观分
ExamSessionService -> MySQL : UPDATE exam_sessions
MySQL --> ExamSessionService : 更新成功
ExamSessionService --> ExamService : 提交成功
ExamService --> ExamController : 提交成功
ExamController --> Frontend : 200 OK
Frontend -> Frontend : 跳转到成绩页
Frontend --> Student : 显示客观题得分

@enduml
